high_descs: Turn left, walk straight to the fridge, turn left when you reach the fridge, walk straight and turn left to face the table.
Pick up the knife on top of the table.
Turn around, then turn right, walk straight to the counter, when you reach the counter turn right, walk straight, then turn around to face the counter.
Open the counter drawer, place the knife inside the drawer and close the drawer.
Turn around, walk straight to the wall, when you reach the wall turn right, walk straight to the wall and turn right to face the table.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn right, walk straight, turn left to face the counter and walk straight to it.
Open the drawer, place the knife beside the other knife in the drawer, and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place two knives in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn to the left and go to the fridge, hang a left and go to the wall, hang a left and go to the dining table.
Pick up the big knife that is on the dining table in front of the bread.
Turn around and then go to the right, go to the drawer that is between the fridge and the stove.
Open the drawer, put the knife inside the drawer, close the drawer.
Turn around and go to the wall, hang a right and go to the dining table.
Pick up the big knife that is on the dining table in front of the bread.
Turn to the right and go past the dining table, then turn to the left and go to the drawer that is between the fridge and stove.
Open the drawer, put the knife inside the drawer, close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two knives in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the fridge, then turn left again and walk over to the round black table.
Pick up the closest large metal knife with a golden handle off of the round black table.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn left again and take another step, after that turn right and walk across the room to where the toaster is on the counter.
Open the drawer below the counter where the toaster is and place the large metal knife inside to the left, then close the drawer.
Turn around and begin across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the wall, then turn right again to face the round black table.
Pick up the large metal knife with a golden handle off of the round black table.
Turn right and walk back over to the part of counter where the toaster is.
Open the drawer to the left of the oven and place the large metal knife inside to right of the knife that is already in there, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two knives into a drawer.

high_descs: turn left and walk forwards to the fridge, then turn left and walk to the black table to the left of you
grab a knife off of the kitchen table there
turn left and walk over to the left side of the kitchen counter on your left
place the knife inside of the pullout drawer on the left side of the kitchen counters
turn left and walk over to the left side of the kitchen table ahead
grab a knife off of the kitchen table again
turn right and walk back over to the left end of the kitchen counters on your left again
place the knife in that same pullout drawer on the left side of the kitchen cabinets
anns.task_desc: place two knife's from the table in the pullout drawer of the kitchen cabinets

high_descs: Move to stand at the black round kitchen table.
Pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle from the table.
Turn and move to stand near the small counter space between the fridge and stove.
Open the top drawer beneath that counter space and place the knife inside.
Move back to stand at the kitchen table, but now on the opposite side of where you were previously.
Pick up the sharp knife by the loaf of bread.
Carry the knife to the counter space between the fridge and stove.
Open the top drawer and place the knife inside to the right of the knife you previously put there.
anns.task_desc: Move two knives to a drawer by the stove.
